    "Before that, we need to know some of your information.\nThis information will used to maximize your personal experience." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "بس أول شي نبي نعرف عنك شوي معلومات.\nبنستخدمها عشان نحسّن تجربتك."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Erzähl uns kurz was über dich.\nDamit machen wir die App genau für dich passend."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Antes de eso, cuéntanos un poco sobre ti.\nLo usamos para que la app encaje contigo."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "On a juste besoin de quelques infos sur toi.\nÇa nous aide à te proposer la meilleure expérience."
          }
        },
        "hi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "उससे पहले थोड़ी सी जानकारी चाहिए।\nइसी से एक्सपीरियंस आपके हिसाब से बनेगा।"
          }
        },
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Sebelum itu, kami butuh sedikit info kamu.\nDipakai biar pengalamannya makin pas buat kamu."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Prima però ci servono un paio di info su di te.\nCosì rendiamo l'esperienza tutta tua."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "その前に、ちょっとだけ教えてね。\nあなたに合った体験にするために使うよ。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "그 전에 몇 가지만 알려주세요.\n맞춤 경험을 만드는 데 써요."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Eerst even wat info over jou.\nZo maken we 't extra leuk voor jou."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Но сначала пара вопросов о тебе.\nЭто чтобы сделать всё под тебя."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "在那之前，告诉我们一点关于你的信息。\n我们用它把体验做得更对你的胃口。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Before that, we need to know some of your information. This information will be used to maximize your personal experience." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Sebelum itu, kami butuh sedikit info kamu. Dipakai biar pengalamannya makin pas buat kamu."
          }
        }
      }
    },
